feat: Initial setup scripts for ChromeDriver installation on Windows
- Added setup.sh for Linux/Mac to check for Python and Google Chrome installation, download and install ChromeDriver. - Created windows-setup.bat for Windows to automate ChromeDriver installation with administrative checks and environment variable setup. - Developed windows-setup.ps1 for PowerShell users to install required packages and set up ChromeDriver. - Introduced test.py script to extract skills from a job description using OpenAI API. - Included author information and licensing details in all new files.

feat: Implement posts and user profile management API
- Added endpoints for creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting posts. - Integrated background analysis for post content using MCP server. - Implemented user profile management with endpoints for viewing and updating profiles. - Established database schema for posts and user profiles in Cassandra. - Configured FastAPI router to include posts and users endpoints. - Enhanced error handling for post and user operations. - Added support for content moderation and sentiment analysis. - Updated documentation to reflect new API structure and features.

Enhance DNA-Flex API with authentication, rate limiting, and background processing
- Implement JWT authentication for protected endpoints - Add rate limiting to key API endpoints - Introduce background processing for DNA sequence analysis - Create detailed error response format for better debugging - Update API documentation to reflect new features and endpoints - Add a web interface with HTML templates for user interaction - Refactor existing endpoints to support new features and improve error handling - Enhance test suite with authentication flow, rate limiting, and concurrent request handling
